sequenceDiagram
participant Client
participant CarController
participant CarService
participant CarRepository
participant Database

    Client->>+CarController: POST /cars
    Note over Client,CarController: CarCreateOrUpdateRequest JSON

    CarController->>CarController: call.receive<CarCreateOrUpdateRequest>()
    
    alt Validatie mislukt
        CarController-->>Client: 400 Bad Request
        Note over CarController,Client: "Error bij aanmaken van DTO"
    end

    CarController->>CarController: ownerId ophalen ("3fa85f64-...")
    
    CarController->>+CarService: createCar(request, ownerId)
    
    CarService->>CarService: Request valideren en Car object maken
    
    CarService->>+CarRepository: create(car)
    
    CarRepository->>+Database: INSERT INTO cars_table
    
    alt Opslaan succesvol
        Database-->>-CarRepository: CarEntity
        CarRepository-->>-CarService: CarEntity
        CarService->>CarService: CarEntity naar Car mappen
        CarService-->>-CarController: Car object
        CarController-->>-Client: 201 Created + Car object
    else Opslaan mislukt
        Database-->>CarRepository: null
        CarRepository-->>CarService: null
        CarService-->>CarController: null
        CarController-->>Client: 500 Internal Server Error
        Note over CarController,Client: "Error bij opslaan in DB"
    end